In This Project we have done operation on CRUD Operations using various Concepts of DRF like

- api guide: view      (https://www.django-rest-framework.org/api-guide/views/)
   - Function based view

1.serialisation : tutorial -> 1-Serialisation
   - serializer: api-guide->serilizer
   - Serializer fields: api-guide -> Serializer fields
2.status code: api-guide status Code
3.validation: api-guide->serilizer -> validation 
    1. field Level
    2. object Level
    3. validator
